---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import ItemCard from "../components/ItemCard.astro";
import MemberCard from "../components/MemberCard.astro";

const menu = await Astro.glob("../content/menu/*.md");

const coffees = menu.filter((item) => item.frontmatter.category === "coffee");
const pastries = menu.filter((item) => item.frontmatter.category === "pastry");
const members = menu.filter((item) => item.frontmatter.category === "member");
---

<MainLayout title="About Us | CozyCup">
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 mx-4">
    <h3 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-12 text-center">Café Story</h3>
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg leading-relaxed">
      <p class="mb-6">
        CozyCup was born out of curiosity for exceptional coffee and a passion
        for creating a space where community and comfort come together. Our
        journey began in the heart of a small town, where our founder, Uzziel,
        transformed an old, charming brick building into a cozy haven for coffee
        lovers.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-6">
        From the very beginning, we were driven by a simple philosophy: to offer
        the finest coffee made from carefully sourced beans, roasted to
        perfection. Our dedication to quality and sustainability has been at the
        core of everything we do, from the selection of our suppliers to the
        brewing methods we use in our café.
      </p>
      <p>
        Today, CozyCup is more than just a place to grab a cup of coffee. It's a
        reflection of our values, a place where every visitor feels at home,
        surrounded by the rich aroma of freshly brewed coffee and the warmth of
        a welcoming atmosphere.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 mx-4">
    <h3 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-12 text-center">Our Team</h3>
    <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-12 md:gap-16 justify-center">
      {
        members.map((item) => (
          <li>
            <MemberCard item={item.frontmatter} />
          </li>
        ))
      }
    </ul>
  </section>
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 bg-gray-100 mx-4">
    <h3 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-12 text-center">Café's Mission</h3>
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg leading-relaxed px-4">
      <p class="mb-6">
        At CozyCup, our mission is simple: to create a cozy and welcoming
        environment where coffee enthusiasts can relax, connect, and savor the
        moment. We believe that a great cup of coffee can brighten your day,
        spark conversations, and build community.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-6">
        We strive to be more than just a café; we want to be a second home for
        our customers, a place where they can escape the hustle and bustle of
        daily life. Whether you're here for a quick espresso, a leisurely latte,
        or one of our freshly baked pastries, we’re committed to providing an
        experience that nourishes both the body and soul.
      </p>
      <p>
        Every cup of coffee we serve is crafted with care, and every interaction
        is an opportunity to make someone’s day a little brighter. This is our
        promise to you, and it’s a mission we’re passionate about fulfilling,
        one cup at a time.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
